(14844, 528, 'biog', '<!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiZWVYUWx0VFRnanoxVUlhWXFyUGVQWW9MIiwicGFzdGVJRCI6LTEsImRhdGFUeXBlIjoic2NlbmUifQo=(/figmeta)--><!--(figma)(/figma)-->Recently nominated for seven Brit Awards and six MOBOs, we are delighted to have Telfords finest performing on the Karma Cola Stage on Friday night.\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Her We Still Believe events are celebratory, inclusive spaces in which various genres of electronic music are acknowledged, with performers &amp; fans all part of a truly engaging and welcoming event.</p>\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9E-d4VPt6cE'),
