(14877, 539, 'biog', '<p class=\"p1\">This artists rise has been stealthy but unstoppable, and the man behind it all, is now one of the biggest electronic artists of our time. 2017s album was his biggest yet, achieving a Top 5 position in the UK and nominated for best Dance/Electronic album at The GRAMMYs, cementing his breakthrough in America.</p>\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_jfHalX5atA'),
