(16208, 607, '_content_segment_0_heading', 'field_5bc830270856b'),
(16209, 607, 'content_segment_0_content', 'There\'s lots of ways you can get to Plot Festival. We\'d encourage you to get the train, coach or car share wherever possible. Have a look below to find out how to get to our beautiful location in the Malvern Hills.'),
