(17911, 638, 'content_segment_0_content', 'Explore what\'s happening at Plot Festival 2019 - it takes places over 4 days, with 3 days of full music programming, in a stunning location in the Malvern hills. We were honoured to win Best New Festival at the UK Festival Awards 2018. To make sure we keep delighting our visitors we\'ve got lots of exciting stuff happening this year. Check out whats in store below.'),
