ovide us with evidence as listed on the form in order to receive your personal assistant ticket.\r\n<h4>2)<b>Viewing Platform Wristband</b></h4>\r\nA viewing platform will be located within the Main Stage arena. In order to gain access to a viewing platform, you need a viewing platform wristband.'),
