(20371, 680, '_content_segment_2_heading', 'field_5bc830270856b'),
(20372, 680, 'content_segment_2_content', 'Take pleasure seriously and check-in to Plot\'s Boutique Village. We believe comfort is a key ingredient to having the best possible weekend, that\'s why we have created a home away from home, in the beautiful surroundings of the Malvern Hills. Take advantage of exclusive facilities, including a 24-hour concierge, porter service, premium toilet and shower facilities, pamper facilities, Boutique Village Bar serving late into the night and a team of experienced and professional staff on hand to make your stay as relaxing as possible.'),
