(26154, 751, 'content_segment_0_content', '<section class=\"article-single wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"content-text-container space-bottom-l content-text \">\r\n<div class=\"wysiwyg-content\">\r\n\r\nGeneral camping is included in your festival ticket (if you have purchased a Camping ticket option), and we have several beautiful camping fields, all of which have stunning views of Eastnor Castle and the surrounding area of natural beauty. Our camping site is secure and serene, an idyllic setting with good facilities. As seasoned festival goers ourselves, and having spent years working on various different festivals before Plot, we understand the importance of an abundance of hot showers, well maintained toilets and fresh drinking water points.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section>\r\n<div class=\"swiper-container quote swiper-container-horizontal swiper-container-fade slider-applied\" data-autoplay=\"5000\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"swiper-slide item swiper-slide-duplicate\" data-swiper-slide-index=\"16\">\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>'),
