(26732, 765, '_content_segment_1_heading', 'field_5bc82ce0de3ec'),
(26733, 765, 'content_segment_1_content', 'You will be allowed 5 x 5 meters of space per camper van pitch to use for your camper van. However, please be aware that water and electricity hook up will not be available, and that campervan tickets must be purchased in advance for site planning purposes.\r\n\r\nCars will not be allowed into the camper van area at anytime so consequently caravans and trailer tents will not be permitted.'),
