(30366, 804, '_content_segment_0_heading', 'field_5bc830270856b'),
(30367, 804, 'content_segment_0_content', 'Eastnor Castlelies in Herefordshire at the foot of theMalvern Hillson the edge of the Cotswolds. Surrounded by a beautiful deer park, arboretum and lake, Eastnor Castle is the homeof the Hervey-Bathurst family.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-790\" src=\"http://plot.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/location2-1024x617.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"617\" />\r\n\r\nBesides being a fascinating and award-winning visitor attraction,Eastnor Castle fulfils other roles as an exclusive-use wedding venue, corporate team building venue, and private party venue, as well as a venue for product launches and location filming.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-791\" src=\"http://plot.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/location1-1024x617.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"617\" />\r\n\r\nVisitors and guests can stay on the estate in either ofthe beautifully refurbished holiday cottages or enjoy camping or caravanning on the Eastnor Deer Park Campsite. Guests who arepart of a wedding, business/corporate or private party can stay in the castles beautiful bedrooms, and our highly professional team is on hand to organise every aspect of your visit.'),
